Very small metro station and not safe. They just finished construction and for now it's back to order. Neighbour hood is a bit dangerous around. You better choose to use Metro Cote Vertu station instead, and then to walk for 3 to 4 minutes to where you are going as destination.
Long, neatly kept metro station that has two exits. Make sure you know which way your headed to save yourself 10-20 minutes of extra walking.
Good for public transport for point claire
Note that there are TWO entrances/exits! The other entrance has no staff, so if you show up there,  you'll have to use the machine to buy a ticket.
Buses usually on time, quite crowded with students leaving from 4-6 PM.
that escalator eventually needs to get fixed.

(Translated by Google) When you are in a bad mood, it is very suitable for a person to walk here, quietly, and then suddenly become clear.

(Original)
心情不好的时候，很适合一个人到这边走走，静静，然后豁然开朗。

(Translated by Google) Second metro of the orange line. It is located between the stations "Côte-vertu" (terminus of the orange line) and "de la Savane". It is served by several buses including the 409 which serves the west of the island.

(Original)
Deuxième métro de la ligne orange. Il se trouve entre les stations "Côte-vertu" (terminus de la ligne orange ) et "de la Savane". Il est desservi par plusieurs bus dont la 409 qui dessert l'ouest de l'île.

(Translated by Google) Escalators walk 1 day out of 2. When you are young no worries but there is still a lot of walking up / down ...

(Original)
Les escalators marchent 1 jour sur 2. Quand on est jeune pas de soucis mais il y a quand même énormément de marche à monter/descendre...

(Translated by Google) Like its neighbors, this station is directly on Décarie. The resort is clean and the art there is unique. From this station you can access a small quiet green area to rest.

(Original)
Comme ses voisines, cette station se trouve directement sur Décarie. La station est propre et l'art qu'on y retrouve eat unique en son genre. De cette station vous pouvez accéder un peit espace vert bien tranquille pour vous reposer.

(Translated by Google) Metro station located just before the coast terminus under the orange line. Staff are on site, the Internet network is functional. There are signs of arrivals and departures. It is usually crowded during rush hour.

(Original)
Station de métro situé juste avant le terminus côte vertu de la ligne orange. Un personnel est en service sur place, le réseau Internet y fonctionnel. On retrouve des panneaux des arrivées et des départs. Elle est généralement bondée aux heures de pointes.

(Translated by Google) Note that until the summer of 2018 there is only the south entrance (corner Cartier and Ouimet) which remains open. The main entrance at the corner of Décarie and the College being repaired. It will be expanded and an elevator installed. The street corner he occupies is barred to traffic.

(Original)
À noter que jusqu'à l'été 2018 il n'y a que l'entrée sud (coin Cartier et Ouimet) qui reste ouvert. L'édicule principal au coin de Décarie et du Collège étant en réfection. Il sera agrandi et on y installe un ascenseur. Le coin de rue qu'il occupe est barré à la circulation.
